The third is that accelerated computing is multi-domain. It=E2=80=99s domai=
n-specific. The algorithms and the software stack that you create for compu=
tational biology, and the software stack that you create for computational =
fluid dynamics are fundamentally different. Each one of these domains of sc=
ience need their own stack, which is the reason why accelerated computing h=
as taken us nearly three decades to accomplish.

This is the software manifestation of the same point: writing parallizable =
